title: Stop the Excuses (Yvonne Orji and Ettore “Big E” Ewen Interview )
itunes:title: Stop the Excuses (Yvonne Orji and Ettore “Big E” Ewen Interview )
description:
Today on the show we had Yvonne Orji stop by where she spoke about talks self love, Insecure's final season, ideal relationships and more. Also they had Ettore “Big E” Ewen stop by where he spoke about being the 4th Black WWE Champ, trust & respect, Vince McMahon and more. Charlamagne gave "Donkey of the Day" to PETA because they want baseball to rename Bullpen, claiming its offensive to cows.
